headline.main: Alliance Passes From Theoretical to the Practical Stage -- 'Special Consideration' Given to Problems of the Balkans

lead_paragraph: ANKARA, Turkey, Feb. 28 -- Behind the phrasing of a brief communique this afternoon, summing up the results of British Foreign Secretary Anthony Eden's visit, is concealed a momentous new development in the Anglo-Turkish alliance.
